<br>
To-date we have assigned group leaders.  I think we should ask Group Leaders to step forward.  The reasons to why I think this is important:<br>
- some people have faster systems.<br>
- some people are faster typers.<br>
- some classes need to concentrate on more important things while in battle that is within their text, so therefore cannot always concentrate on chat.<br>
- it allows the person who offered to take responsibility, as opposed to us assigning it.<br>
<br>
There are challenges to being a Group Leader.  As well a Group Leader is not a prestigous &lt;sp&gt; right, it's a position who is comfortable in being able to keep their group together, keeping up with the commands, etc.    <p><img src="http://werzat.freeservers.com/dsig3c.gif">
